<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.5">
<l>māta vaṉeṉ maṇiyiṉai valaiyiṟ piḻaitta paṉṟipōl</l>
<l>ētu moṉṟuṅ koḷattārā vīcaṉ ṟaṉṉaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>pītaka vāṭai yuṭaitāḻap peruṅkār mēkak kaṉṟēpōl</l>
<l>vīti yāra varuvāṉai viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see Mādhava, my Sapphire, the Supreme Lord who</l>
<l>Gives nothing at all for another, like a boar that escaped from the nets?</l>
<l>We saw Him in Bṛndāvana come so that the street [looked] full,</l>
<l>Like the calf of a big, dark cloud, in such a way that [His] yellow robes hung low!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
